Task 1: Basic Task

~$ ls
~$ pwd
~$ mkdir workspace
~$ cd workspace
~$ ls
~$ touch README.md
~$ cp README.md ./CHANGELOG.md

Task 2: Absolute and Relative Paths

~$ touch exercise.md
~$ mv exercise.md /tmp/
~$ rm /tmp/exercise.md

Task 3 : cat commands

~$ cat > umuzi.md
~$ cat > recruits.md
~$ cat > cohorts.md
~$ cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohorts.md
~$ cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohorts.md -> summary.md
~$ cat summary.md
  
Task 4: Locate commands

$ locate umuzi
~$ locate umuzi.md > search_results.md
~$ cat search_results.md

Task 5: The locate command cont..

$ cd Documents
~$ touch pad.md
~$ ls
~$ mv pad.md ~/Documents
~$ cd ~/Desktop
~$ mkdir work
~$ cp pad.md pad_copy.md
~$ locate updatedb
~$ cd 
~$ locate pad_copy.md
~$ ls

Task 6 Find commands

~$ find ~/ -name *.pdf
~$ mv /home/recruit/Downloads/sample.pdf ~/Download
~$ cd ~/Downloads
~$ find -mtime -1 -ls

Task 7: Text editor
~$ nano my_bio.md
$ ls
$ mkdir my_files.md
$ mv my_bio.md my_files.md
$ ls













